import React from 'react'
import Accordion from './Accordion'
import { Description, Heading, Main, MainGrid, MainImage, Shortheading, Subgrid, Subheading } from './Whatwedo.element'

function Whatwedo() {
    return (
        <Main>
           <MainGrid>
               <MainImage>

               </MainImage>

               <Subgrid>
                <Shortheading>WHAT WE DO</Shortheading>
                <Heading>We Provide Flexible IT Services</Heading>
                <Subheading></Subheading>
                <Description><Accordion></Accordion></Description>
               </Subgrid>
            </MainGrid> 
        </Main>
    )
}

export default Whatwedo
